        { "speaker": "A", "chinese": "我叫小丽。认识你很高兴！", "pinyin": "Wǒ jiào Xiǎo Lì. Rènshi nǐ hěn gāoxìng!", "english": "My name is Xiao Li. Nice to meet you!" },
